## 0.4.0 (2023-05-22)

### New feature:

-   **原生支持 Wayland 取词**([`55c3bd1`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/55c3bd1a7a0153a081dc0b7241c2d9696befba34)) (by Pylogmon)
